<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/table.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/nav.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/home">
            <img src="./img/now_logo.png" alt="로고 사진 입니다.">
        </a>
        <div class="menu">
            <p class="nav-intro" style="margin-top:25px;">
                <%=user[0].nickname%>님 정보수정 페이지
            </p>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <hr>
    닉네임 : <%= user[0].nickname %>
    <br>
    이메일 : <%= user[0].email%>
    <br>
    이름 : <%= user[0].user_name%>
    <br>
    정보를 수정하시려면 올바른 비밀번호를 입력하여 주십시오.
    <form action="/user/identify" method="POST">
        <input type="password" name="user_passowrd" id="user_passowrd">
        <input type="submit" value="정보수정하기">
    </form>
    
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th class="table-header"><%= user[0].nickname %>님이 쓴 게시글 목록</th>
        </tr>
        <% if (post.length > 0) {%>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <% for( var i = 0; i< post.length; i++) { %>
                        <form action="/post/<%= post[i].id%>" method = "POST" style="padding-bottom: 5px; padding-top: 5px;">
                            <input type="submit" name="post_title" id="post_title" class="title" value="<%= post[i].title %>">
                        </form>
                        <hr>
                    <% } %>
                </td>
            </tr>
        <% } else { %>    
            <td>
                작성한 게시글이 없습니다!
            </td>
        <% } %>     
    </table>
</body>
</html>